  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a008/17/2017 3:02 CT (16:02 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.2-DuplicateSubmits\">Duplicate Submits</h2><p>We added\u00a0protection against importing the same file twice, creating an invoice twice, and saving an RMA batch twice</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.2-TicketView-ReturnButton\">Ticket View - Return Button</h2><p>Fixed logic that would hide the return button on the ticket view too aggressively.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.2-StoreCreditUpdates\">Store\u00a0Credit Updates</h2><p>In some cases you could apply the same store credit transaction to the customers running credit balance. This has been resolved.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.2-DeviceNotesParagraphMargins\">Device Notes Paragraph Margins</h2><p>We have reduced the margins between paragraphs/line breaks in device notes to restore the margins that existed before the text editor was updated.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.2-TextEditorSpellcheck\">Text Editor Spellcheck</h2><p>Browser spellcheck is now no longer disabled\u00a0inside the text editor fields (notes, diagnostics, etc)</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
